name: CG5
description: '''Charles Duncan Green V''' (born May 10, 1999), also known professionally as '''CG5''', is an American singer-songwriter, [[Record producer|music producer]], and [[YouTuber]]. He started on [[YouTube]], making [[nerdcore]] [[hip-hop]] songs about various topics relating to video games and [[internet culture]]. He is also the director of the horror series and film hybrid ''[[Project U Move]]''.
